In this guide I will be installing Windows 11 on a unsupported machine, I will be using a HP Elite 8300 which has an Intel i5 3rd gen, TPM 1.2&hellip;
This Elite 8300 supports UEFI and Secure Boot, also pass the RAM and GHz requirements, you can bypass these ones too but I would recommend to have 8GB or more RAM for Windows 11 (or any machine running in 2021-2022).
1. Getting the Insider Preview file First, you will need to get the ISO file.
